Node class Design

# Purpose of the Node class
- To represent the locations of the grid

# Main attributes
- NodeID (String): Unique identifier for each node.
- Name (String): Label
- Type (String): Role in the grid (Ex: Generator, Consumer)

# Main methods
. __post_init__ () --> validate the dataclass
. get_info() --> returning the node details
. connection (Node) --> allow nodes to connect
. get_connections () --> returns the connected list of nodes
